{"h5138a572g0886g4797ga9e3g9345daf23c4c": ["*The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Dead.html", "799059e0-808c-edda-3b88-32fa6f2264c7"], "h29cdfefcg03f7g490dg8ad6ga7524812fb34": ["*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Dead.html", "a107de05-7a31-f170-f958-cedabaf7373f"], "h69ad5682gf93cg4854g8d9fge751445da52a": ["*With a gasp, the corpse shudders.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Dead.html", "ea8ced2e-6896-e526-414b-8563943dca04"], "h25c1fb67g1ab1g44f5g817dg3b93d7949a16": ["... it's gone... finally...", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Dead.html", "1e452795-1218-0da6-2bc0-de13a1e00347"], "h5de0c052g5b44g4fecgb052g70015139a916": ["What's gone?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Dead.html", "e0f377f2-11b3-e858-04a0-b89b7ac4100e"], "h96b8a2c3gead2g42ddgac7aga1814c908a42": ["The sight...", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Dead.html", "3bfc1a9c-0820-55fb-a595-c80be88015df"], "hd6fb10a6gf053g4f8eg8e31gfec2f2ceaa4d": ["... I could see... a person's fate... <i>horrible.</i>", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Dead.html", "1e28b71e-d05e-968d-c232-377320848ef2"], "h4293587ag1b20g4ee3g81fbg59904e2e63eb": ["Who are you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Dead.html", "377149d7-01b3-b306-3560-fda3cb55ea7c"], "hbb4789a5g5fc4g4d58g86f7g66a613fce746": ["Father... husband... son...", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Dead.html", "d66d41c0-ba73-f0c8-4588-e5bf01ffd1cf"], "h584acc5fg5a5fg4d41gb7ccge19fc9db07b4": ["... but... no more. I am Lorin... only...", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Dead.html", "d5af552c-0da4-5540-6795-c979fdcf1f0c"], "h42459872gbf0dg42ecg8aedgdc81ee496129": ["How did you end up in the cave?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Dead.html", "4e7e42ef-64c4-9763-9167-f7449279380f"], "h15626694gc139g4a48g890fgfa2af1c82946": ["Trapped... between two choices... I made a deal... to see my fate... ", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Dead.html", "7a63ee63-d259-2209-7fd3-176c895d5212"], "hb14010cfgc990g49a6ga41fg689f4f5dd7a9": ["... but all I saw... was <i>death</i>... so I ran... ran here...", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Dead.html", "1c68fd86-1cf3-d7c2-8ca7-3a366b4e0395"], "hc31a507bg8479g4063g82b1g46e4a308a645": ["What can you tell me about the hag?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Dead.html", "697d2af7-714f-aa0c-8495-e2198e9a360a"], "he3b56b7bgfce8g4041g9e8ag491f0f6b68e8": ["... she gives you... exactly what... was promised...", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Dead.html", "210f7714-59c4-7d24-3f75-3209a282ecce"], "hfc85cb68g039fg45efga89fg83f7996099bc": ["Do you regret making a deal with the hag?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Dead.html", "43154b62-bae3-dbfd-c819-9e210efe7ddc"], "had6073c9g0580g43dbg9effg39ae19ea0f61": ["Making a... deal? Yes. Being... here...? No. ", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Dead.html", "7b04092b-a840-0621-7151-24d377f1d181"], "h953bba76g942eg4c9fgb33cge94c750993b6": ["Here... I couldn't see it... couldn't see... my family... dead and rotten.", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Dead.html", "79094b48-cdec-abb5-569b-ab5a78266a31"], "haa798ac8g2234g4b7bga021g0663c7e2ad3c": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Dead.html", "90f5323b-b575-e394-7503-0292125bf755"], "h45efd890gfb24g415dg895fg8993a39db20a": ["*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Dead.html", "aa667b3a-4d5e-ca02-c35d-d93a5019a80a"]}